    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Fixing Eclipse Can Not Find Java on Ubuntu]]></title>
    <link href="http://andylinid45.github.io/blog/2015/08/22/fixing-eclipse-can-not-find-java-on-ubuntu/"/>
    <updated>2015-08-22T11:10:58+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://andylinid45.github.io/blog/2015/08/22/fixing-eclipse-can-not-find-java-on-ubuntu</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>gedit ECLIPSE_HOME/eclipse.ini # add below before &lsquo;-vmargs&rsquo;
<code>
-vm
/usr/lib/jvm/jdk1.8.0_51/bin/java
</code></p>

<p><a href="http://wiki.eclipse.org/Eclipse.ini">http://wiki.eclipse.org/Eclipse.ini</a></p>
]]></content>
